{"tid":676031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"昆凌進軍荷里活 🙄","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T18:35:37.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cee13417e0b1c43e8ae14bbea0e9f77b7ae83d7e","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xUN1de1Tsro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxUN1de1Tsro&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=66787135\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xUN1de1Tsro</a><br />\n<br />\n嫁周董咁有米唔喺屋企湊仔<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf4dc140b9892100732c1a0c3fe8b9c30e170b31","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"說到台灣女星昆凌，大家第一個想到的可能會是她的老公周杰倫，但其實在結婚之前她就已經拍過多部電視劇及電影，但可惜作品大部分只在台灣播映，因此未能讓更多人看見她精湛的演技。直到去年,傳出昆凌將參演由 The Rock 擔任男主角的荷里活災難大片《Skyscraper》(摩天大樓)，消息曝光後讓外界相當期待，畢竟已經很久沒有看見昆凌在螢光幕上演出了，這回究竟要挑戰什麼樣的角色呢？"},{"pid":"58b34c082e8e408b9134325ba1307fcb3f7db69b","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"這次她在片中要挑戰詮釋一位冷酷無情的女殺手，從先前曝光的劇照看來，不管是造型、眼神 還是高難度的動作戲，都完全顛覆了以往昆凌嬌滴滴的印象，只看照片還不夠，如今官方片花 終於曝光,霸氣又性感的模樣讓人差點認不出來，大讚昆凌真的好會演啊!(昆凌畫面在 0:56 開始)"},{"pid":"33d3ef5e6f6e39d60f101e9a2ff57692dfc01f76","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"其實昆凌的好演技其來有自，原來她高中就畢業於表演藝術科系，大學時也曾到紐約進修電影 製作及電影表演相關課程，不只實力堅強，昆凌的敬業態度也相當受到讚賞,早在 《Skyscraper》還未結束拍攝時,男主角 The Rock 就曾在 IG 上分享他與昆凌的合照,並大 讚：「很榮幸和昆凌合作,也等不及讓全世界看到我們合作的電影,她總是充滿能量,做得好Hannah！」隨後附上hashtag: 「#她很危險也很致命」從她的亮眼表現看來,這或許不是昆 凌最後一部荷里活電影喔!《Skyscraper》將在 7 月 13 日上映，準備好見識不一樣的周太太了沒？"},{"pid":"b8883725deb6b547b887769c4560aae07ddf068c","tid":676031,"uid":139322,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"rock 到底拍左幾多套題材有關災難既片"},{"pid":"08ae5ea4598eb6eef5e2edb989ce1577b10b1aec","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"傳奇影業（英語：Legendary Pictures, Inc.；也稱為「傳奇娛樂」）是一個美國的電影製片公司，總部位於加州柏班克。公司成立於2000年，由托馬斯&middot;圖爾創建，2005年該公司與華納兄弟電影公司達成了一項協議，擁有聯合製作和資助40部影片；合同到期後轉為與環球影業合作。2016年1月，被<span style=\"color: red;\">萬達集團</span>以35億美元的價格收購<br />\n<br />\n原來支資公司黎？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dee6cbb842ce03862d0dc6a35f6ee847cea12290","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":52,"dislike":7,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/98f21df5366b190132bc39db3bd21f0d/5BBEE985/t51.2885-15/e35/22794036_1560147764047885_4487281474654961664_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F98f21df5366b190132bc39db3bd21f0d%2F5BBEE985%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F22794036_1560147764047885_4487281474654961664_n.jpg&h=4b7a5ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇落好似鬼妹<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11d114528ac516670dfdc8414d8f193610bb15c4","tid":676031,"uid":3405,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"dee6cbb842ce03862d0dc6a35f6ee847cea12290","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":52,"dislike":7,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"