人眼睛為之一亮。<br />\n<br />\n佢幾時開始拍武打 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba9d8b2a24086156e398dd53ceeda677c80f283","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"這也是昆凌生完第2胎羅密歐，產後僅3天就開始工作，由周杰倫親自為愛妻拍試鏡帶爭取到的角色。之前巨石強森提及昆凌，讚她「自我約束力很強，非常勤勞，性格好」，還不忘提及開心見到周董，引來話題。<br />\n<br />\n導演和編劇是由曾經指導《中央情爆員》和《全家就是米家》勞森‧馬修‧托波，主要演員有夯爆全球的巨石強森《玩命關頭8》、妮芙‧坎貝爾《驚聲尖叫4》、帕布羅‧薛伯《13小時：班加西的秘密士兵》"},{"pid":"df2e544dc6f943e7bc8ddd54d941b14ef2408f0b","tid":676031,"uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"28a7c49736e6d3c2b4a277916fb5ee5e82ac0574","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚樣衰，成個墨西哥妹咁</blockquote><br />\n我覺得一時時，有時睇落又好似ok😄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"樣一般<br />\n性格幾好<br />\n回記者好得體"},{"pid":"f4f3e026d1f41859e32a05d7ef7dbb0a0ed50b3c","tid":676031,"uid":33104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"df2e544dc6f943e7bc8ddd54d941b14ef2408f0b","tid":676031,"uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"28a7c49736e6d3c2b4a277916fb5ee5e82ac0574","tid":676031,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚樣衰，成個墨西哥妹咁</blockquote><br />\n我覺得一時時，有時睇落又好似ok😄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"樣一般<br />\n性格幾好<br />\n回記者好得體"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"性格幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前睇黑澀會佢假到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d8dd1b15b8b4838e75ebbfab72909525a11197","tid":676031,"